                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Même jusqu'à Madagascar\nSon nom était parvenu, car\nC'était selon tous les principes\nQu'après les cercles de papier,\nSans jamais les estropier\nIl traversait le rond des pipes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Il s'élevait à des hauteurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Telles, que les autres sauteurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Se consumaient en luttes vaines.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ils le trouvaient décourageant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et murmuraient : \" quel vif-argent",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Ce démon a-t-il dans les veines ? \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il s'élevait à des hauteurs\nTelles, que les autres sauteurs\nSe consumaient en luttes vaines.\nIls le trouvaient décourageant,\nEt murmuraient : \" quel vif-argent\nCe démon a-t-il dans les veines ? \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Tout le peuple criait : \" bravo ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Mais lui, par un effort nouveau,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Semblait roidir sa jambe nue,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Et, sans que l'on sût avec qui,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Cet émule de la saqui",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Parlait bas en langue inconnue.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout le peuple criait : \" bravo ! \"\nMais lui, par un effort nouveau,\nSemblait roidir sa jambe nue,\nEt, sans que l'on sût avec qui,\nCet émule de la saqui\nParlait bas en langue inconnue."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "C'était avec son cher tremplin.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Il lui disait : \" théâtre, plein",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "D'inspiration fantastique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Tremplin qui tressailles d'émoi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Quand je prends un élan, fais-moi",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Bondir plus haut, planche élastique !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'était avec son cher tremplin.\nIl lui disait : \" théâtre, plein\nD'inspiration fantastique,\nTremplin qui tressailles d'émoi\nQuand je prends un élan, fais-moi\nBondir plus haut, planche élastique !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "\" frêle machine aux reins puissants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Fais-moi bondir, moi qui me sens",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Plus agile que les panthères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Si haut que je ne puisse voir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Avec leur cruel habit noir",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Ces épiciers et ces notaires !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" frêle machine aux reins puissants,\nFais-moi bondir, moi qui me sens\nPlus agile que les panthères,\nSi haut que je ne puisse voir\nAvec leur cruel habit noir\nCes épiciers et ces notaires !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "\" par quelque prodige pompeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Fais-moi monter, si tu le peux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à ces sommets où, sans règles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Embrouillant les cheveux vermeils",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Des planètes et des soleils,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Se croisent la foudre et les aigles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" par quelque prodige pompeux,\nFais-moi monter, si tu le peux,\nJusqu'à ces sommets où, sans règles,\nEmbrouillant les cheveux vermeils\nDes planètes et des soleils,\nSe croisent la foudre et les aigles."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "\" plus haut encor, jusqu'au ciel pur !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à ce lapis dont l'azur",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Couvre notre prison mouvante !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'à ces rouges orients",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Où marchent des dieux flamboyants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Fous de colère et d'épouvante.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" plus haut encor, jusqu'au ciel pur !\nJusqu'à ce lapis dont l'azur\nCouvre notre prison mouvante !\nJusqu'à ces rouges orients\nOù marchent des dieux flamboyants,\nFous de colère et d'épouvante."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "\" plus loin ! Plus haut ! Je vois encor",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Des boursiers à lunettes d'or,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Des critiques, des demoiselles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Et des réalistes en feu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Plus haut ! Plus loin ! De l'air ! Du bleu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Des ailes ! Des ailes ! Des ailes ! \"",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" plus loin ! Plus haut ! Je vois encor\nDes boursiers à lunettes d'or,\nDes critiques, des demoiselles\nEt des réalistes en feu.\nPlus haut ! Plus loin ! De l'air ! Du bleu !\nDes ailes ! Des ailes ! Des ailes ! \""
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
